Product: Clinora
Module: Doctor Management & Scheduling
Document Type: Product Requirements Document (PRD)
Version: 1.0
Status: Draft

1. Purpose

The Doctor Management & Scheduling module enables clinics to onboard doctors, configure consultation schedules, manage availability, assign specialties, define consultation fees, and control appointment slots.

This module serves as the scheduling engine for Clinora and directly supports appointment booking, consultations, prescriptions, laboratory requests, billing, and analytics.

2. Business Objective

Provide clinics with a centralized system to:

Manage doctor profiles
Configure consultation schedules
Generate appointment slots
Prevent double booking
Handle doctor leave and holidays
Improve patient scheduling
Maximize doctor utilization
3. Scope
