4. Actors
Actor	Responsibilities
Clinic Admin	Creates and manages doctors
Reception	Views schedules and books appointments
Doctor	Views and updates availability
Patient	Searches available doctors
System	Generates appointment slots and validates availability
5. User Stories
US-DOC-001

As a Clinic Admin,

I want to create a doctor profile,

so that the doctor can consult patients.

US-DOC-002

As a Clinic Admin,

I want to configure the doctor's weekly schedule,

so appointments can be booked automatically.

US-DOC-003

As a Doctor,

I want to request leave,

so patients cannot book appointments during my absence.

US-DOC-004

As a Patient,

I want to see available doctors,

so I can choose the most suitable one.

US-DOC-005

As a Receptionist,

I want to see today's doctor schedules,

so I can efficiently manage bookings.

