7. Functional Requirements
FR-DOC-001 Doctor Profile

Each doctor profile shall contain:

Employee ID
Name
Photo
Qualification
Registration Number
Specialization
Department
Experience
Biography
Consultation Fee
Languages Spoken
Status
FR-DOC-002 Weekly Schedule

Configure:

Monday

09:00 AM - 01:00 PM

02:00 PM - 06:00 PM

Repeat for all weekdays.

FR-DOC-003 Slot Duration

Supported:

10 Minutes

15 Minutes

20 Minutes

30 Minutes

45 Minutes

60 Minutes
FR-DOC-004 Consultation Types

Support:

Physical Visit
Video Consultation (Future)
Home Visit (Future)
FR-DOC-005 Availability

Doctor status:

Available

Busy

On Leave

Holiday

Inactive
FR-DOC-006 Break Time

Support:

Lunch Break

Tea Break

Custom Break

Example:

09:00 - 01:00

Break

01:00 - 02:00

02:00 - 06:00
FR-DOC-007 Leave

Support:

Casual Leave
Sick Leave
Vacation
Emergency Leave

During leave:

No new appointments
Existing appointments flagged
Reception notified
FR-DOC-008 Holidays

Clinic holidays automatically block doctor schedules.

FR-DOC-009 Doctor Search

Search by:

Name
Department
Specialization
Language
Availability
FR-DOC-010 Doctor Dashboard

Display:

Today's appointments
Current patient
Upcoming appointments
Pending lab reports
Follow-ups
Revenue summary (optional)
Patient queue
8. Business Rules
Every doctor belongs to one clinic in MVP.
Every doctor has one schedule.
Appointments cannot overlap.
Slot duration is configurable.
Leave overrides working schedule.
Holidays override schedules.
Inactive doctors cannot receive bookings.
Consultation fees may vary by doctor.
