12. Validation Rules

Doctor Name

Required

Maximum 100 characters

Consultation Fee

Must be positive

Schedule

Cannot overlap

Break

Must fall within working hours

Leave

Cannot overlap existing leave

13. Security

Only Clinic Admin can:

Create doctors
Delete doctors
Configure schedules

Doctors can:

View profile
Update limited personal information
Apply leave

Patients

Read-only access to public doctor information required for booking.

