19. Acceptance Criteria

This module is complete when:

Clinic Admin can create and manage doctors.
Doctors have configurable weekly schedules.
Appointment slots are generated correctly.
Double booking is prevented.
Leave blocks appointment booking.
Holidays block appointment booking.
Patients can search available doctors.
Reception can view doctor schedules.
APIs match the OpenAPI specification.
All changes are audited.
Multi-tenant isolation is enforced.
